description: This file defines the application's route configuration using React Router, mapping URL paths to corresponding page components. It includes a healthcheck route displaying a JSON status and various application pages like Dashboard, Planner, Tracker, MindMood, Coach, Settings, and a NotFound fallback. It also imports configuration from an environment variables module.

methods.name: AppRoutes()
methods.description: Defines and returns the routing structure for the application, including a healthcheck endpoint.

methods.name: HealthRoute
methods.description: A React component that provides a simple health status JSON output for monitoring.
